<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <title>Shipping Policy | VASKA</title>
</head>
<body class="px-16 tracking-wide bg-[#FAF8F0] text-[#1e1e19] font-[Montserrat]">
    <%- include('partials/topbar') %>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto my-10 p-6 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Shipping Policy</h1>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">At VASKA, we strive to deliver your orders efficiently and on time. Please review our shipping policy below.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">1. Shipping Methods</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We offer the following shipping methods to ensure timely delivery:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
            <li>Standard Shipping: 5-7 business days</li>
            <li>Express Shipping: 2-3 business days</li>
            <li>Same-Day Delivery (available in select locations)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">2. Shipping Charges</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Shipping costs vary based on the delivery location and selected shipping method. The applicable charges will be displayed at checkout.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">3. Order Processing Time</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Orders are processed within 24-48 hours, excluding weekends and public holidays.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">4. International Shipping</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We currently ship to select international destinations. Delivery times and charges vary based on location.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">5. Delayed or Lost Shipments</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
            <li>If your order is delayed, we will notify you via email.</li>
            <li>For lost shipments, please contact our support team within 14 days of the expected delivery date.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">If you have any questions regarding our shipping policy, please <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 underline">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>